※各々数量に限りがあります。早期完売の際は悪しからずご了承ください。

※バッテリープラス側端子カバーへの挿入のしやすさを考慮して、純正バッテリー端子固定ボルトよりも幅狭のY型端子(φ4)を採用しております。端子の先開部をボルトネジ山に沿って挿し込み、横に広げたY型端子が不用意に抜けない状態で確実に取り付けてください。
※付属のスロットルスリーブはリブ無しタイプの純正類似品です。スロットル開度は純正と若干異なりますので、予めご了承ください。
※消費電力約18W。駐停車時には都度スイッチを切り、車両のバッテリー上がり、長時間連続使用による低温火傷には十分注意してください。
※リレー本体やスイッチ、ハーネスなど、この商品の構成部品は完全防水設計ではありません。ご使用期間の多寡によらず、雨水や浸水などによる部品故障は保証対象外です。

■詳細説明
ALU-BOX silver 45/37
The tough TRAX ADVENTURE touring cases accept any challenge: Embossed designs add to the stability of the welded aluminum walls with a thickness of 1.5 millimeters. The removable lid with anodized aluminum carrying handles and quick release fastener allows easy loading and unloading of the watertight touring cases. A lateral chamfer on the outer case edge provides ground clerance while cornering.
This set consists of two TRAX ADVENTURE motorcycle side cases，also included are QUICK-LOCK EVO side carriers，adapters and locking system at an attractive price point. Carrier and case configuration have been carefully selected to complement the motorcycle models tail geometry and exhaust system. Once installed the QUICK-LOCK EVO carrier can be removed within a heartbeat. Also available for the vesatile carrier platform are adaptations for other case brands.
Features TRAX ADVENTURE side cases
・Tough and watertight aluminum motorcycle cases
・Anodized surface prevents aluminum residue under all climate conditions
・Completely removable lid with quick release fastener and opening limiter
・4 large tie-down points，integrated into the lid geometry
・Outer chamfer for best ground clearance while cornering
・Corner caps made from glass reinforced plastics
・Embossed designs，deep-drawn lid and welded body provide high stability
・Steel hinges
・Exchangeable sealing gasket
・Can be combined with ALU-RACK and TRAX ADVENTURE top case
・Dimensions left case (45 l): 49 x 28 x 37 cm
・Dimensions right case (37 l): 49 x 23 x 37 cm
Features QUICK-LOCK EVO side carrier
・Robust steel construction with black powder coating
・Quick release fasteners allow carrier mounting and removal within seconds
・Unobtrusive installation points at the bike frame
・Designed for case mounting close to the motorcycle
・Can also be used together with other case brands
・Width without cases: 480 mm

■詳細説明
ALU-BOX EN (2) silver 37/37
The tough TRAX ADVENTURE touring cases accept any challenge: Embossed designs add to the stability of the welded aluminum walls with a thickness of 1.5 millimeters. The removable lid with anodized aluminum carrying handles and quick release fastener allows easy loading and unloading of the watertight touring cases. A lateral chamfer on the outer case edge provides ground clerance while cornering.
This set consists of two TRAX ADVENTURE motorcycle side cases，also included are QUICK-LOCK EVO side carriers，adapters and locking system at an attractive price point. Carrier and case configuration have been carefully selected to complement the motorcycle models tail geometry and exhaust system. Once installed the QUICK-LOCK EVO carrier can be removed within a heartbeat. Also available for the vesatile carrier platform are adaptations for other case brands.
Features TRAX ADVENTURE side cases
・Tough and watertight aluminum motorcycle cases
・Anodized surface prevents aluminum residue under all climate conditions
・Completely removable lid with quick release fastener and opening limiter
・4 large tie-down points，integrated into the lid geometry
・Outer chamfer for best ground clearance while cornering
・Corner caps made from glass reinforced plastics
・Embossed designs，deep-drawn lid and welded body provide high stability
・Steel hinges
・Exchangeable sealing gasket
・Can be combined with ALU-RACK and TRAX ADVENTURE top case
・Dimensions left case (37 l): 49 x 23 x 37 cm
・Dimensions right case (37 l): 49 x 23 x 37 cm
Features QUICK-LOCK EVO side carrier
・Robust steel construction with black powder coating
・Quick release fasteners allow carrier mounting and removal within seconds
・Unobtrusive installation points at the bike frame
・Designed for case mounting close to the motorcycle
・Can also be used together with other case brands
・Width without cases: 420 mm

ALU-BOX black 45/37
The tough TRAX ADVENTURE touring cases accept any challenge: Embossed designs add to the stability of the welded aluminum walls with a thickness of 1.5 millimeters. The removable lid with anodized aluminum carrying handles and quick release fastener allows easy loading and unloading of the watertight touring cases. A lateral chamfer on the outer case edge provides ground clerance while cornering.
This set consists of two TRAX ADVENTURE motorcycle side cases，also included are QUICK-LOCK EVO side carriers，adapters and locking system at an attractive price point. Carrier and case configuration have been carefully selected to complement the motorcycle models tail geometry and exhaust system. Once installed the QUICK-LOCK EVO carrier can be removed within a heartbeat. Also available for the vesatile carrier platform are adaptations for other case brands.
Features TRAX ADVENTURE side cases
・Tough and watertight aluminum motorcycle cases
・Powder coated surface prevents aluminum residue under all climate conditions
・Completely removable lid with quick release fastener and opening limiter
・4 large tie-down points，integrated into the lid geometry
・Outer chamfer for best ground clearance while cornering
・Corner caps made from glass reinforced plastics
・Embossed designs，deep-drawn lid and welded body provide high stability
・Steel hinges
・Exchangeable sealing gasket
・Can be combined with ALU-RACK and TRAX ADVENTURE top case
・Dimensions left case (45 l): 49 x 28 x 37 cm
・Dimensions right case (37 l): 49 x 23 x 37 cm
Features QUICK-LOCK EVO side carrier
・Robust steel construction with black powder coating
・Quick release fasteners allow carrier mounting and removal within seconds
・Unobtrusive installation points at the bike frame
・Designed for case mounting close to the motorcycle
・Can also be used together with other case brands
・Width without cases: 500 mm

■詳細説明
ALU-BOX black 37/37
The tough TRAX ADVENTURE touring cases accept any challenge: Embossed designs add to the stability of the welded aluminum walls with a thickness of 1.5 millimeters. The removable lid with anodized aluminum carrying handles and quick release fastener allows easy loading and unloading of the watertight touring cases. A lateral chamfer on the outer case edge provides ground clerance while cornering.
This set consists of two TRAX ADVENTURE motorcycle side cases、also included are QUICK-LOCK EVO side carriers、adapters and locking system at an attractive price point. Carrier and case configuration have been carefully selected to complement the motorcycle models tail geometry and exhaust system. Once installed the QUICK-LOCK EVO carrier can be removed within a heartbeat. Also available for the vesatile carrier platform are adaptations for other case brands.
Features TRAX ADVENTURE side cases
・Tough and watertight aluminum motorcycle cases
・Powder coated surface prevents aluminum residue under all climate conditions
・Completely removable lid with quick release fastener and opening limiter
・4 large tie-down points、integrated into the lid geometry
・Outer chamfer for best ground clearance while cornering
・Corner caps made from glass reinforced plastics
・Embossed designs、deep-drawn lid and welded body provide high stability
・Steel hinges
・Exchangeable sealing gasket
・Can be combined with ALU-RACK and TRAX ADVENTURE top case
・Dimensions left case (37 l): 49 x 23 x 37 cm
・Dimensions right case (37 l): 49 x 23 x 37 cm
Features QUICK-LOCK EVO side carrier
・Robust steel construction with black powder coating
・Quick release fasteners allow carrier mounting and removal within seconds
・Unobtrusive installation points at the bike frame
・Designed for case mounting close to the motorcycle
・Can also be used together with other case brands
・Width without cases: 540 mm
